Cospan-equiv‚Üźcomponents = _‚ČÉ_.bwd Cospan-equiv‚ČÉcomponents

components‚ÜźCospan-equiv
  : ‚ąÄ {ūĚď§ ūĚď• ūĚď¶ ūĚď§' ūĚď•' ūĚď¶'} {S : Cospan ūĚď§ ūĚď• ūĚď¶} {T : Cospan ūĚď§' ūĚď•' ūĚď¶'}
    ‚Üí Cospan-equiv S T ‚Üí Cospan-equiv-components S T
components‚ÜźCospan-equiv = _‚ČÉ_.fwd Cospan-equiv‚ČÉcomponents

opaque
  Cospan-equiv-is-torsorial
    : ‚ąÄ {ūĚď§ ūĚď• ūĚď¶} (S : Cospan ūĚď§ ūĚď• ūĚď¶)
      ‚Üí is-singleton (ő£ (Cospan ūĚď§ ūĚď• ūĚď¶) (Cospan-equiv S))
  Cospan-equiv-is-torsorial S
    = is-single‚Üźequiv-to-single
        (ő£-‚ČÉ (Cospan-repr‚ČÉ e‚ĀĽ¬Ļ) őĽ x ‚Üí Cospan-equiv‚ČÉcomponents e‚ĀĽ¬Ļ)
        (is-singleton-structure‚Üźparts
          (SingS-is-single (Cospan.Centre S))
          (_ , idequiv)
          (is-singleton-structure‚Üźparts
            (SingS-is-single _)
            (_ , idequiv)
            (is-singleton-structure‚Üźparts
              (SingS-is-single _)
              (_ , ~refl)
              (is-singleton-structure‚Üźparts
                (SingS-is-single _)
                (_ , idequiv)
                (SingS-is-single _)))))

Cospan-equiv‚ÜźId-is-equiv
  : ‚ąÄ {ūĚď§ ūĚď• ūĚď¶} {S T : Cospan ūĚď§ ūĚď• ūĚď¶} ‚Üí is-equiv (Cospan-equiv‚ÜźId {S = S}{T})
Cospan-equiv‚ÜźId-is-equiv
